[normal]Written evidence from Susan Atkinson
[normal]My husband and I farm in south Notts, on an 80 hectare farm that has been in my husband’s family for over 90 years.  At present it is mostly arable and also in the HLS scheme.  My husband and I are also volunteers with the Farming Community Network (FCN).
